cur_data.desc: Open House Sunday April 29th, 11:30am-1:00pm. Located in North Randolph, close to public transportation and major highways, this Cape home includes 3 good sized bedrooms with high ceilings, 2 Full Bath plus the much desired 1/2 Bath. Unloading groceries is a snap as the kitchen is close to exterior access. Once your meal has been prepared you may choose to dine on the 3 season enclosed porch off the kitchen or to the Formal Dining Room. Before turning-in, gather around the newly painted Living Room with large Picture Window, decorative Brick Fireplace and well maintained Hardwood Floors and Wood Trim throughout. Bonuses include Large Deck off the Enclosed Porch and partially Finished Basement with Full Bath. Additionally, lovely conservation area and nature trails close by.

Welcome home! This property has the best of it all - Dead end street, cul de sac, and LOCATION! Beautiful home in Autumn Woods. Come and see this lovely 2800 SF colonial perfect for entertaining that sits 75’ back from the street. 2 Story open foyer, 28’ living room with fireplace and in wall surround sound hookup. Beautiful center island kitchen overlooking landscaped yard. Head down stairs to great room perfect for a large party or just family time. Lovely master bedroom with master bath and walk in closet! You don’t want to miss this one!

Desirable Randolph neighborhood! This colonial home is full of charm, featuring a custom kitchen with granite, beamed ceiling, hardwood floors, updated bath and a whole lot more. First floor master and three additional rooms on the second floor. Partially finished basement with family/media room that walks out through a sun porch to a private yard. Newer roof, siding, electric and blown in insulation. Showings begin at the open house!

Spacious solid 4 bedrooms Colonial.  Appealing updated kitchen with island. Awesome hardwood flooring in living room, dining room and bedrooms. Newer windows.  Quiet neighborhood.  Close to shopping, restaurants, school, bank, etc. This is a Short-Sale transaction.  All Terms are Subject to Third Party Lender Approval.  Property to be sold 'as is' 'as seen' 'where is', seller/listing agent make no warranties or representations. Buyer responsible for any and all inspections necessary to complete sale.  Buyer (or their agents) shall perform own due diligence. Sale and Offer should specify subject to buyer paying off Seller's liens of $30,000 at closing.

Welcome to Westminster Arms! Enter this spacious and freshly painted top floor 2 bedrooms 1 bath unit with laminate flooring throughout and a beautiful kitchen that offers granite countertop and stainless steel appliances. A wonderful and serene condominium complex that is conveniently located close to everything. A short distance to supermarkets, restaurants, convenience stores, shopping, public transportation, access to the highway, and much more while being tucked away in a quiet, charming neighborhood away from the busy main street. Enjoy relaxing on the balcony or at the condominium’s inground pool which is perfect for the summer days!

Don't miss this Adorable single family house. Located in a very desirable Randolph neighborhood right over the Milton line. The completely renovated interior boasts Newly Refinished Hardwood Floors. Gorgeous Kitchen with Marble Countertops, and all new Stainless Steel Appliances. The bathroom is tastefully remodeled with style that pops. This single family home includes a double lot of 10,000 sq ft combined! This size lot gives homeowner a large side yard with future possibilities. BRAND-NEW ROOF! Brand New Windows throughout. BRAND NEW GAS FURNACE. Conveniently located in a quiet side street right off of major highways 93/95. Extremely accessible to restaurants, supermarket, shops, parks, bus routes and at the end of the street there are actually horse stables! This house is maintenance free and MOVE IN READY!

Stunning Colonial with all the bells and whistles!!!  This 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom home has all the extras, including, Maple Kitchen Cabinets, Red Oak Hardwood Floors, (2) Fireplaces, 4" Crown Molding, Recessed Lighting and Central A/C.  As beautiful as the inside is, the extras continue outside, where you'll enjoy the convenience of a large tool shed, with electricity, spacious patio and brand new stockade fence.  This home is minutes from the commuter rail and and a short drive to several major highways, including 24,93, & 3.  This home won't last long, so please make it a point to stop by at one of our two weekend Open Houses!

A beautiful house for a small family with a lot of Character.Large living room,large eating kitchen,Large Master bedroom with half bath,hardwood floor,nice enclosed back yard and a lot more.Itwon`t last.Bring your buyers for a quick sale.

Absolute Bargain... all Located in a Cul-de-sac! Unbelievable Price! Priced low & firm for your pre-approved buyer who wants a great value on the best house in YOUR TOWN! This house has all good size bedrooms, finished basement for family entertainment and a bonus room can be used as an office or a bedroom, and central heat.  In-ground heated well-lit pool.  Pool house has an outdoor shower.  One(1)car garage and off-street parking spaces, short distance to Randolph High School and Shaws Supermarket. Easy access to public transportation and highway. It won’t last long at this low, low price, so hurry and do your buyer a favor & write me a clean, full price offer today & save yourself all the fun of a full price counter offer!  ALL OFFERS DUE BY MONDAY 4/30/18 3:00 p.m.

This inviting  7 room, 4 bed 2 bath home sits nestled on a wooded lot on a private street. Perfect location being close  to both highways and trail ways for recreation. It's in Pristine condition. This home shows true Pride of Ownership! A beautiful kitchen w and Shaker design wooden cabinets, Sill Stone Counter tops and gorgeous tile flooring. Open dining room with sliders that lead to a wood deck that overlooks a large back yard. Perfect for entertaining friends and family. Bright sun filled living room with brick fireplace and hard wood floors, first floor bath has nice Bear Claw Tub /Separate shower and Double sinks!  3 bedrooms on upper level with wall to wall carpet, One currently being used as an office. Downstairs you are transported to a beautiful Master bedroom Suite with track lighting,walk in closet/updated attached bathroom. A  nice size family room, laundry room and plenty of storage. This is a lot of house!
